can add equal tomato and onion (3 to 2) or something.

similar to paneer butter masala. Add chickpea to pressure cooker. Morning itself soak chickpeas for full day. Then wait for 3-4 whistles. 
Oil, cumin seed, onion and chili. Ginger garlic one spoon. One spoon of chili powder, one spoon coriander, 1/5 haldi, namak accordingly,
then add chana masala. Fry and then add tomato. When the tomato leaves the water, add to drained chickpeas.

